than the incidents, and I'm curious what the differentiation

40:41.318 --> 40:42.700
is between those two.

40:44.590 --> 40:48.540
Okay, Mr. Smith, you're going to have to repeat the second part of

40:49.070 --> 40:52.590
your question, the first one in regards to staffing,

40:53.970 --> 40:57.066
look, I've made several presentations to the Public Safety

40:57.098 --> 41:01.322
Committee. I made the same presentation

