42:00.718 --> 42:04.654
us at 350 firefighters that we're going to be hiring

42:04.782 --> 42:08.550
this fiscal year. That is, in attempts to

42:08.620 --> 42:12.882
make up for what we lost in 2019 and 2020. Our normal

42:12.946 --> 42:15.320
annual attrition is about 170.

42:15.930 --> 42:19.750
That's retirements, that's resignations. That's everything else

42:19.820 --> 42:23.718
about 170. We're having to hire 100 above

42:23.734 --> 42:26.906
and beyond the normal attrition to try to make up for what we

42:26.928 --> 42:29.500
lost again in 2019 and 2020.

