a resident of Cynic Wood neighborhood in northeast Houston,

47:27.068 --> 47:30.132
which is District B. I'd like to thank the Chief for his

47:30.186 --> 47:33.476
leadership. I have a few questions for him, but first a

47:33.498 --> 47:37.376
statement. I want him to thank Al Bennett,

47:37.488 --> 47:41.396
who has made sure that my community has gotten carbon monoxide detectors

47:41.428 --> 47:44.724
and smoke detectors and continues to do so recently.

