47:48.228 --> 47:51.924
cycle chief, you mentioned to this committee that you had a significant

47:51.972 --> 47:55.756
number of engines in your fleet that were in disrepair. You were

47:55.778 --> 47:58.920
waiting on new engines, and you were also seeking

47:59.000 --> 48:03.032
to technology, but you're also waiting to seek

48:03.176 --> 48:06.704
more training for your firefighters. You've addressed these points in

48:06.742 --> 48:09.920
some of the questions that were posed to you today. But again,

48:10.070 --> 48:14.064
the theme is, can you reiterate has

48:14.102 --> 48:17.828
any of these issues been addressed at this point? That's the first question.

